// ChatToggle
// Fixed-position button that opens and closes the chat drawer.
// Shows an unread message count badge when the drawer is closed and there are unread messages.

FUNCTION ChatToggle(props) -> ReactNode                                   EXPORT
  Renders a circular button fixed to the edge of the screen.
  IF the drawer is open, shows a close icon; otherwise shows a chat bubble icon.
  IF unreadCount > 0 and the drawer is closed, overlays a red badge with the count.
  Calls onToggle when clicked.
